{
  "title": "ISic003648. I.Sicily inscription 003648",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἀφροδ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀφροδ\"><span data-text=\"Ἀφροδ\">Ἀφροδ</span></span></span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>ΙΤ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἀφροδ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀφροδ\"><span data-text=\"Ἀφροδ\">ΑΦΡΟΔ</span></span></span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>ΙΤ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003648_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2006-04-24\" src=\"ISic003648_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003648.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2006-04-24\" src=\"ISic003648-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Preliminary text from autopsy</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Suggested to be a dedication to Aphrodite, but it is unclear how much is lost on the right, and whether there were letters before the ΙΤ on line 2. The stone appears never to have been formally published, and there is no clear reference which can be aligned to it in the summary of Scibona on Mistretta in the BTCGI.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.  </div>",
