      "html": "<div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἀφροδ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀφροδ\"><span data-text=\"Ἀφροδ\">Ἀφροδ</span></span></span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>ΙΤ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἀφροδ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀφροδ\"><span data-text=\"Ἀφροδ\">ΑΦΡΟΔ</span></span></span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>ΙΤ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div>"
